民接纳）展开“建设性的对话”。 美国政府的公开表态和媒体报道都显示，美国国务院在过去几个月里一直在公开宣称中国在新疆“屠杀”穆斯林，并在通过美国的官方喉舌和一众大外宣媒体疯狂造势，哪怕中国方面已经用大量证据多次证明了这是一个由美西方势力编造的彻头彻尾的政治谣言。 其中，如今表示希望中国“接纳”阿富汗难民的美国国务院发言人普莱斯，在今年3月还曾明确表示说，美国政府“坚持认为”中国在新疆“屠杀”穆斯林。"},"attached_info":"CkAIwa3Mq5fWycBuEAMaCDY5NTk0MzUwIJa0ookGMPMBOLAZQCZyCTQ4MjkwNjAxN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-b80214fc7d779aa9cf278d5654cb9a15_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"39_1630163217.2934992","card_id":"Q_436868073","target":{"id":436868073,"title":"2021 年，疫苗能结束新冠大流行吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/436868073","type":"question","created":1609141454,"answer_count":183,"follower_count":1271,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[237,18012,19149,227896,566991],"comment_count":20,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Iwa3Mq5fWycBuEAMaCDU5MzYwNDkwIM6Zpv8FMBQ49wlAJ3IJNDM2ODY4MDczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1d963fa475b84d7b5b4b8e36ca6a2fff_1440w.jpg?source=172ae18b"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"40_1630163217.293948","card_id":"Q_312570374","target":{"id":312570374,"title":"哪个瞬间让你突然不爱一个你深爱的人了？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/312570374","type":"question","created":1550367680,"answer_count":296,"follower_count":780,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[740,1211,1525,4728,152180],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Iwa3Mq5fWycBuEAMaCDMxNzM2Nzg5IMD3ouMFMAM4jAZAKHIJMzEyNTcwMzc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"childr